text: Korosey Yalli Moominiinik iisa Siinih yaceem kaa esserteenik Nummah esserten iisa siinih temeeteh bukaa kee xixxibaane sin geyte waqdi, koroosannuu kee Nabii qeebik taadeenim, toysa woh addunyaay akeeral kayrih siinih tayseh, Nabii Mucammad qeebih qagitteenik kay catoo kee kay qokoluh qaktennooh sin butta tamaggeeway tu siinih maxiqta, diggah Yalli catoo kee Qokoluh yeemene mar√¢ luk yan
